  kuralExplanation1:'Who once were his, and then forsook him, as before Will come around, when cause of disagreement is no more.',
  kuralExplanation2:'Those who have been friends and have afterwards forsaken him, will return and join themselves (to him), when the cause of disagreement is not to be found in him.',
  kuralAudio:'529.wav',
