  chapterNumber:'60',
  sectionName:'Wealth',
  kural:'sidhaivitaththu olkaar uravoar pudhaiyampiR pattuppaa toondrunG kaLiRu',
  kuralExplanation1:'The men of lofty mind quail not in ruins fateful hour, The elephant retains his dignity mind arrows deadly shower.',
