  kural:'anpin vizhaiyaar poruLvizhaiyum aaidhotiyaar insol izhukkuth tharum',
  kuralExplanation1:'Those that choice armlets wear who seek not thee with love, But seek thy wealth, their pleasant words will ruin prove.',
