  sectionName:'Wealth',
  kural:'porutpeNtir poimmai muyakkam iruttaRaiyil Edhil piNandhazheei atru',
  kuralExplanation1:'As one in darkened room, some stranger corpse inarms, Is he who seeks delight in mercenary womens charms!.',
