  sectionName:'Wealth',
  kural:'anpunhaaN oppuravu kaNNoattam vaaimaiyodu aindhusaal oondriya thooN',
  kuralExplanation1:'Love, modesty, beneficence, benignant grace, With truth, are pillars five of perfect virtues resting-place.',
